{"tid":1391154,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[學術討論] 聽過太陽同放大鏡既都入入黎阻阻你地","createTime":"2019-07-31T10:46:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T14:41:51.000Z","uid":283781,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"3c29080dc1d4bafdda36dca3865adeece2d970fa","tid":1391154,"uid":283781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T10:46:47.000Z","msg":"真係純學術研究唔好諗過多呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如題 呢個原理我相信好多人讀書都讀過<br />\n咁直接入正題 <br />\n經過放大鏡既太陽光個聚焦點係可以著火既<br />\n咁如果我張個聚焦點放塊鏡<br />\n又可唔可以射去第二度再燒(圖1)<br />\n定係反射左會散返開(我記得好似係咁)(圖2)<br />\n定係會燒著塊鏡呢<br />\n如果用三稜鏡又得唔得<br />\n如果2樣都唔得<br />\n仲會唔會有野可以儲到聚焦點既能量再反射出去<br />\n<br />\n1.<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q3zcDfa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ3zcDfa.png&h=8bb671b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2.<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ySrVA13.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FySrVA13.png&h=c3504fe1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二個方法<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w9GObCh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw9GObCh.png&h=1725a153&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我知個距離有d遠<br />\n個conflex lens度數應該要細細地<br />\n我諗眼鏡鏡片得唔得<br />\nLaser又夠唔夠力<br />\n<br />\n利申中學程度physics  已經比返哂老師<br />\n求physics jj賜教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"273df7f0d5b9da3055fd4ed014e583efe3d701c2","tid":1391154,"uid":283781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T10:47:11.000Z","msg":"唉 仆街開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a81d1e99eec92684a6e4e7fc88724328177460d","tid":1391154,"uid":283781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T10:47:42.000Z","msg":"推到有physics jj入黎幫我上堂"},{"pid":"faad343986d1c6dd6cb0743af2eeae4118590002","tid":1391154,"uid":283781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T10:48:28.000Z","msg":"圖片簡陋屌細力小